sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant FE as Frontend SPA
    participant FA as Firebase Auth
    participant API as Cloud Run API
    participant US as userService (quota)
    participant GH as GitHub API
    participant GM as Gemini API
    participant FS as Firestore

    User->>FE: Submit analyze form
    FE->>FA: Get/refresh ID token
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/analyze (Bearer token + payload)
    API->>API: authenticateUser middleware
    API->>US: consumeAnalysisQuota(uid) [transaction]
    US-->>API: allowed / remaining / tier
    API->>GH: Fetch user repos + snapshots
    GH-->>API: Repo signals
    API->>GM: generateContent(prompt)
    GM-->>API: JSON-like analysis output
    API->>API: Parse + schema validate + sanitize
    API->>FS: Save analysis under users/{uid}/analyses
    FS-->>API: analysisId
    API-->>FE: analysisResult + tone + rateLimit + analysisId
    FE-->>User: Render results page
